<h1>About PTPd (IEEE-1588) on Concerto</h1>
<p>
Texas Instruments has implemented the Open Source PTPd software on its Concerto
family of microcontrollers.  This implementation uses the lwIP TCP/IP stack,
and does not require an RTOS.
</p>
<p>
Details on the Open Source PTP Protocol Software can be found at
<a href="http://ptpd.sourceforge.net">ptpd.sourceforge.net</a>.
</p>
<p>
Details on the Open Source lwIP TCP/IP stack can be found at
<a href="http://www.sics.se/~adam/lwip/">www.sics.se/~adam/lwip/</a>.
<p>
The current IEEE 1588 Time (GMT) is:  Www Mmm Dd, Yyyy  Hh:Mm:Ss
